{"Id":687940,"Title":"和陶诗 答庞参军","Dynasty":"明","Author":"李贤（原德","Context":"林下优游，伴我惟书。有琴一张，聊以自娱。尚志伊何，居我广居。不求闻达，终矣敝庐。惟儒何有，席上之珍。治人有道，各亲其亲。卷而藏之，何求于人。江上之鸥，与尔为邻。学如不及，古人孜孜。人百其能，已则千之。所业伊何，读书诵诗。伊既学矣，云胡不思。今宵风月，与子平分。我有旨酒，欢然交欣。孰云郢歌，遏此行云。古人之妙，今则不闻。干将失雌，在匣常鸣。与子相别，潸然涕零。子之文章，步武西京。何以教我，毋惜丁宁。君子之德，草上之风。执其两端，于民用中。必得其名，高朗令终。子其勉旃，用省厥躬。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"9c67a8ad27fa87983e9c8783f51cdbf1","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6607504,"Sentence":"林下优游，伴我惟书。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǐn xià yōu yóu ，bàn wǒ wéi shū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607505,"Sentence":"有琴一张，聊以自娱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu qǐn yī zhāng ，liáo yi zì yú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607506,"Sentence":"尚志伊何，居我广居。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shàng zhì yī hé ，jū wǒ ān jū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607507,"Sentence":"不求闻达，终矣敝庐。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú qǐu wén dá ，zhōng yi bì lú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607508,"Sentence":"惟儒何有，席上之珍。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi rú hé yǒu ，xǐ shǎng zhī zhēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607509,"Sentence":"治人有道，各亲其亲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhì rén yǒu dāo ，gě qīn jī qīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607510,"Sentence":"卷而藏之，何求于人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"juǎn ér cáng zhī ，hé qǐu yú rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607511,"Sentence":"江上之鸥，与尔为邻。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jiāng shǎng zhī ōu ，yú ěr wéi lǐn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6607512,"Sentence":"学如不及，古人孜孜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xué rú bú jǐ ，gǔ rén zī zī ","Tag":null,"Explanation"